  "help_title": "Page Help \/ Instructions",
  "help_text": "<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\\\"><b style=\\\"line-height: 1.42857;\\\"><span lang=\\\"EN-US\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\\\" tahoma\\\",\\\"sans-serif\\\";=\\\"\\\" mso-fareast-font-family:calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;color:red;=\\\"\\\" text-transform:uppercase;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;=\\\"\\\" mso-bidi-language:ar-sa\\\"=\\\"\\\">SOCIAL LINKS<\/span><\/b><\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\\\"><b style=\\\"line-height: 1.42857;\\\"><span lang=\\\"EN-US\\\" style=\\\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\\\" tahoma\\\",\\\"sans-serif\\\";=\\\"\\\" mso-fareast-font-family:calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;color:red;=\\\"\\\" text-transform:uppercase;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;=\\\"\\\" mso-bidi-language:ar-sa\\\"=\\\"\\\"><br><\/span><\/b><b><span lang=\\\"EN-US\\\" style=\\\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\\\" tahoma\\\",\\\"sans-serif\\\";mso-ansi-language:=\\\"\\\" en-us\\\"=\\\"\\\">DESCRIPTION:<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\\\"><span lang=\\\"EN-US\\\" style=\\\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\\\" tahoma\\\",\\\"sans-serif\\\";=\\\"\\\" mso-ansi-language:en-us\\\"=\\\"\\\">Here you can find the list of your site\/s. You can add\r\nyour Social Links to any site. <o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;\r\nmargin-left:35.4pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal\\\"><span lang=\\\"EN-US\\\" style=\\\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\\\" tahoma\\\",\\\"sans-serif\\\";mso-ansi-language:=\\\"\\\" en-us\\\"=\\\"\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\/o:p><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal\\\"><b><span lang=\\\"EN-US\\\" style=\\\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\\\" tahoma\\\",\\\"sans-serif\\\";mso-ansi-language:=\\\"\\\" en-us\\\"=\\\"\\\">HOW TO USE:<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/b><\/p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\\\"EN-US\\\" style=\\\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\\\" tahoma\\\",\\\"sans-serif\\\";=\\\"\\\" mso-fareast-font-family:calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:=\\\"\\\" en-us;mso-fareast-language:en-us;mso-bidi-language:ar-sa\\\"=\\\"\\\">To add your Social\r\nLinks, just click on the ADD\/EDIT button and you will be able to digit your\r\ncompany social links to allow other users to follow you. These social links\r\nwill be displayed under your Site banner on your e-commerce site.<\/span>"
